
  Ninjask    Bug Type Pokémon

  NINJASK moves around at such 
  a high speed that it cannot be 
  seen, even while its crying can 
  be clearly heard.  For that reason, 
  Ninjask was long believed 
  to be invisible. 
	Evolution Chain
      Nincada ► Ninjask

